        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Sustainable Water Infrastructure Investment Act of 201</strong><b>8</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to exempt tax-exempt facility bonds for sewage and water supply facilities from the state volume caps on private activity bonds.</p>]]></text>
